00:14:08,664 --> 00:14:09,799
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan menunggumu.</font>

236
00:14:12,602 --> 00:14:13,669
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan lupa.</font>

237
00:14:44,800 --> 00:14:46,002
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa yang kau lakukan?</font>

238
