280
00:17:21,257 --> 00:17:23,826
<font color=#FFFF00>Bukankah menurutmu
aku cukup beruntung?</font>

281
00:17:27,063 --> 00:17:28,631
<font color=#FFFF00>Astaga.</font>

282
00:17:28,631 --> 00:17:31,133
