288
00:17:47,016 --> 00:17:48,317
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa kau mengerti atau tidak?</font>

289
00:17:50,586 --> 00:17:51,754
<font color=#FFFF00>Diam!</font>

290
00:17:52,321 --> 00:17:53,956
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Antara paha dan
