297
00:18:15,544 --> 00:18:16,879
<font color=#FFFF00>"Letnan Satu Lee So Won."</font>

298
00:18:16,879 --> 00:18:19,682
<font color=#FFFF00><i>- Untuk wanita, 15 persen...</i>
